[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     11[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The draft file `chapter12.01-appointment-volume-forecasting.md` is not present in the iter-335 worktree at the time of this review. The full recipe content was authored in iter-323 (task `ch12-r01-draft`, marked `passing` in `tasks.json`) and is recoverable from `logs/iter-0323.log`, lines 124–711, where the entire file body was emitted by the writer's `fs_write` create operation. This review evaluates that content. If the file is missing from the worktree at edit time, the editor must restore it from that source before applying the findings below.
