[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    138[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    139[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Severity:** MEDIUM
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    140[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Expert:** Networking (defense in depth, no-egress-to-public-internet for PHI workloads)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    141[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Location:** Prerequisites table, VPC row: "Production: SageMaker training jobs in VPC mode with VPC endpoints for S3 and ECR; Glue jobs in VPC connection where source data is private."
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    142[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Problem:** The recipe lists VPC endpoints for S3 and ECR only. A fully VPC-isolated deployment of this pipeline needs additional interface endpoints to keep all API traffic on the AWS backbone instead of routing over the public internet (still TLS-encrypted, but BAA/PHI workloads conventionally avoid public-internet egress for service-plane traffic). The full set for this pipeline is: S3 (gateway), DynamoDB (gateway), KMS (interface), CloudWatch Logs (interface), CloudWatch Monitoring (interface), SageMaker API (interface), SageMaker Runtime (interface), Glue (interface), Step Functions (interface), and Secrets Manager (interface) if any pipeline secrets are used. ECR is correctly called out for SageMaker bring-your-own-container; ECR Docker (interface) is also needed. Without these, a SageMaker training job inside a VPC reaches the SageMaker control plane via a NAT gateway (or fails outright if no NAT is provisioned), which is the wrong shape and creates a single egress chokepoint.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    143[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Fix:** Replace the VPC row with: "Production: SageMaker training jobs in VPC mode (private subnets, no NAT) with VPC endpoints for S3 (gateway), DynamoDB (gateway), KMS, CloudWatch Logs, CloudWatch Monitoring, SageMaker API, SageMaker Runtime, Glue, Step Functions, and ECR/ECR-Docker (for bring-your-own-container). Glue jobs in VPC connection where source data is private." This is the standard set for a fully isolated AWS ML pipeline and matches the recipe's own elevation of PHI-pipeline discipline.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    144[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
