[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    150[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Problem:** External weather data (NWS, Open-Meteo, paid APIs) and local-event data come from third-party APIs that need outbound HTTPS egress and may have their own BAA considerations (typically not, since aggregate weather data is not PHI, but the *combination* of "this clinic at this location got X inches of snow" is potentially identifying for a small clinic). The recipe lists these as optional features without addressing the egress path or the BAA implication.
